<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-37-0418 </DOCNO><TEXT>This chapter describes experimental and theoretical investigation of thewave action in exhaust and intake manifolds. The initial examples arefor single-cylinder engines, and more complex arrangements are introducedlater. The final part of the chapter describes simulations for turbochargeddiesel engines and naturally aspirated gasoline engines.</TEXT></DOC>